OL,5,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FSeries favourite "Coco" has a new
OL,7,     Frescue - a black stallion he has
OL,8,     Fnamed Black Beauty, who has
OL,9,     Fmedical problems and needs some
OL,10,     Fcareful attention from Colin and
OL,11,     Fhis Spanish vet Antonio.
OL,12,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,13,     FWe meet again with series
OL,14,     Ffavourite Colin "Coco" Brown, who
OL,15,     Fwe usually see working hard at the
OL,16,     Fanimal rescue centre and farm he
OL,17,     Fruns with his partner Sebastian
OL,18,     Fand son Hugo.
