OL,5,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,6,     FCatching up with the victims and
OL,7,     Fvillains of the rental market.
OL,8,     FRachel intended to rent out her
OL,9,     Fcottage for three months; four
OL,10,     Fyears later, her tenant is still
OL,11,     Fthere.
OL,12,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FIn North Yorkshire, cops are out
OL,14,     Fin force, protecting lorry drivers
OL,15,     Fand their cargo as organised gangs
OL,16,     Ftarget goods and trucks. Ther's a
OL,17,     Fhijack on an HGV carrying
OL,18,     F#1million of goods.
