OL,5,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FOn a busy Bank Holiday weekend, a
OL,7,     Fday trip to Scarborough turns into
OL,8,     Fa high-speed pursuit and a
OL,9,     Fdesperate suspect on a motorbike
OL,10,     Fputs lives at risk when a
OL,11,     Fpassenger falls off.
OL,12,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FA car thief rams the cops off the
OL,14,     Froad, a gang travel into North
OL,15,     FYorkshire for some high-end
OL,16,     Fshoplifting, and a suspected scrap
OL,17,     Fmetal thief claims he's running a
OL,18,     Flegitimate business.
