OL,5,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FArmed police respond to reports of
OL,7,     Fa fight involving machetes. Plus,
OL,8,     Fcops provide a dawn chorus (aka
OL,9,     Fraid).
OL,10,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,11,     FPolice enter a 'house of horrors'
OL,12,     Fseeking a man on the run. Plus, an
OL,13,     Fepic 45-mile pursuit.
