OL,5,G1700 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,6,     FUndercover detective Steve tails
OL,7,     Ftwo suspects who previously evaded
OL,8,     Fcapture, and later deals with a
OL,9,     Fwoman suspected of stealing
OL,10,     Fthousands of pounds' worth of
OL,11,     Fperfume. (Ep3)
OL,12,G1800 Home and Away
OL,13,     FCash and Eden find a compromise.
OL,14,     FMackenzie breaks down. Mali tricks
OL,15,     FJohn.
OL,16,G1830 Home and Away
OL,17,     FMackenzie and Levi struggle to
OL,18,     Fprocess their grief. Lacey worries
OL,19,     Ffor her dad. Richie visits David.
