OL,5,G1900 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FIt's a busy night at Barnsley
OL,7,     FHopsital's casualty department, so
OL,8,     Fwhen Sister Benita arrives to head
OL,9,     Fthe shift, the corridors are
OL,10,     Falready packed full of patients.
OL,11,G2000 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,12,     FIn Birmingham, Jane is fed up with
OL,13,     Fa painful rash on her scalp;
OL,14,     FMyfanwy has concerns that her mum
OL,15,     Fmay have sepsis after a procedure;
OL,16,     Fand Jean discusses her mental
OL,17,     Fhealth struggles.
